                                    <br /> 9. Notice of cancellation of the sale will be delivered to buyers by phone and / or e-mail address mentioned on the registration page.
                                    <br /> 10. The product ran out of stock after you make a sale, are allowed to store and / or supplier to cancel the sale and / or offer alternative product of equal value.
                                    <br /><!>  Notice of cancellation shall be stated in writing or by telephone<!>.
                                </p>
                            </div>
